---
title: DataCite - Technical documentation
---

<header class="image-bg-fixed-height-small">
  <div class="jumbotron">
    <h1>
      Technical Documentation
    </h1>
  </div>
</header>

<section>
  <div class="container section-content">
    <h1>service integration</h1>
    <p>
      This Technical Documentation section provides information on how to
      handle or integrate DataCite services. It is available openly and
      supplies detailed descriptions of functionality and architecture for both
      production and labs services.
    </p>
    <p>
      Should you have any question or request, please
      <%= link_to 'contact us', 'contact.html' %>!
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
<section>
  <div class="container-fluid bg-primary">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-12">
        <h1 class="svc-heading">How to...</h1>
      </div>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="row text-center">
          <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 svc-item">
            <div class="thumbnail">
              <div class="caption" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#mds">
                <h2>Assign DOIs (MDS)</h2>
              </div>
              <div id="mds" class="collapse documentation">
                <ul>
                  <li>Schema: <%= link_to 'DataCite Metadata Schema',
                    'https://schema.datacite.org/' %>
                  <li>API documentation: <%= link_to 'MDS API Doc',
                    'https://mds.datacite.org/static/apidoc' %>
                  <li>DOI Documentation: <%= link_to 'DOI Handbook',
                    'http://doi.org/10.1000/182' %>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 svc-item">
            <div class="thumbnail">
              <div class="caption" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#search">
                <h2>Search</h2>
              </div>
              <div id="search" class="collapse documentation">
                <ul>
                  <li>Traditional search: <%= link_to 'Search examples and UI',
                    'http://search.datacite.org/ui' %>
                  <li>New labs search: <%= link_to 'Common API',
                    'https://api.datacite.org' %>
                  <li>Common DataCite API development:
                    <%= link_to 'Github',
                    'https://github.com/datacite/spinone/issues' %>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="row text-center">
          <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 svc-item">
            <div class="thumbnail">
              <div class="caption" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#event">
                <h2>Event data</h2>
              </div>
              <div id="event" class="collapse documentation">
                <ul>
                  <li>New labs search: <%= link_to 'Common API',
                    'https://api.datacite.org' %>
                  <li>Common DataCite API development:
                    <%= link_to 'Github',
                    'https://github.com/datacite/spinone/issues' %>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-md-6 col-sm-12 svc-item">
            <div class="thumbnail">
              <div class="caption"
                    data-toggle="collapse"
                    data-target="#re3data">
                <h2>re3data</h2>
              </div>
              <div id="re3data" class="collapse documentation">
                <ul>
                  <li>Schema: <%= link_to 'Schema 3.0 XML Schema',
                    'http://doi.org/10.2312/re3.009' %>
                  <li>Schema documentation: <%= link_to 'Schema 3.0
